**Do I need rental references for ANU off-campus housing as a first-time renter?**
Yes, most **ANU private rental options** require references, but first-time renters can substitute character references from academic supervisors, employers, or volunteer coordinators. The ANU Student Accommodation Services team provides reference templates and can issue letters confirming enrollment status to strengthen applications.

